{
  "id": "10025",
  "key": "GG-22",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "Establish Clear Logging and Progress Status for Migration Tasks",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use case:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As a "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Product Owner",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "I want to ensure clear logging and progress status for the migration tasks, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "so that the development team can monitor and troubleshoot the migration process effectively."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance criteria:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "GIVEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the migration task is initiated,"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "WHEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the task starts executing,"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AND",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " progress is made,"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "THEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the backend should log each step and update the front end with the current status."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Technical notes:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The backend should utilize logging frameworks to record each stage of the migration process, including fetching issues, workflows, screens, and custom fields. It should also provide real-time updates to the front end using WebSocket or polling mechanisms. The progress status should be clear and easily understandable by users and other teams involved in the migration. All logs should adhere to security best practices and not expose any sensitive data."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
